diff: +		* Feature in Internet Explorer.  Stopping pending requests when no request has been
+		* issued causes a default 'Action cancelled' page to be displayed.  Since Stop must
+		* be issued here, the workaround is to first Navigate to the about:blank page before
+		* issuing Stop so that the 'Action cancelled' page is not displayed.

members.signatureBeforeChange: public boolean setUrl(String url, String postData, String headers[])
members.signatureAfterChange: public boolean setUrl(String url, String postData, String headers[])
